mixin cta-second(data)
    section.cta.cta_second&attributes(attributes)
        .cta__container.container
            .cta__row
                .cta__col
                    h2.cta__title.title Не нашли <br/>то что искали?

                    .cta__text Обратитесь к нашему менеджеру заполнив форму или воспользуйтесь фильтрами.
                        != pugHelpers.Icon.call(locals, {iconName: 'arrow', className: 'cta__arrow'})

                    .cta__filter.filter-panels
                        h2.filter-panels__title
                            != pugHelpers.Icon.call(locals, {iconName: 'select-panels', className: 'filter-panels__icon'})
                            | Выбрать другие панели:

                        form(action="").filter-panels__form.form
                            .filter-panels__row.form__row
                                .filter-panels__field.form__field.form__field_checkbox
                                    label.form__label
                                        input.form__checkbox(type="checkbox" name="" value="" checked)

                                        span.form__label-text бюджетные

                                .filter-panels__field.form__field.form__field_checkbox
                                    label.form__label
                                        input.form__checkbox(type="checkbox" name="" value="" checked)
                                        span.form__label-text негорючие


                                .filter-panels__field.form__field.form__field_checkbox
                                    label.form__label
                                        input.form__checkbox(type="checkbox" name="" value="" checked)
                                        span.form__label-text износостойкие

                                .filter-panels__field.form__field.form__field_checkbox
                                    label.form__label
                                        input.form__checkbox(type="checkbox" name="" value="" checked)
                                        span.form__label-text влагостойкие

                                .filter-panels__field.form__field.form__field_checkbox
                                    label.form__label
                                        input.form__checkbox(type="checkbox" name="" value="" checked)
                                        span.form__label-text трудногорючие

                                .filter-panels__field.form__field.form__field_checkbox
                                    label.form__label
                                        input.form__checkbox(type="checkbox" name="" value="" checked)
                                        span.form__label-text антивандальные


                            input.filter-panels__submit.button(type="submit" value="Применить")

                .cta__col
                    .cta__form
                        .cta__form-w
                            .cta__form-title.title.title_second Остались вопросы?

                            form(action="" method="")
                                .form__field.form__field_label_text
                                    label.form__label Имя
                                        input.form__input(type="input" name="" value="" checked)

                                .form__field.form__field_label_text
                                    label.form__label Фамилия
                                        input.form__input(type="input" name="" value="" checked)

                                .form__field.form__field_label_text
                                    label.form__label Телефон
                                        input.form__input(type="input" name="" value="" checked)

                                .form__field_submit
                                    input.cta__form-submit.form__submit.button(type="submit" value="Отправить")

